Cell["\<\
and then to execute (repeatedly,  to gain a sense of the situation) the \
series of 100 commands that are presented below.

REMARK: I have been unable to devise a master command that generates those \
sequential commands automatically, was forced to write them out by hand.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.535743266501903*^9, 3.535743398011145*^9}}],

